真诚朋友，中方积极参与伊拉克经济重建，各领域友好务实合作稳步推进。 \t8月，伊拉克总理办公室宣布，伊政府与中国电建签署了建设2000兆瓦光伏电站的协议。 \t据中国驻巴格达大使馆介绍，伊拉克现在是中国在中东投资的主要目的地，主要是石油行业。中国是伊拉克石油的最大买家。 \t中国企业还计划伊拉克建设更多基础设施，包括电力供应、通信、学校、供水、机场和铁路等。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IjO27uMfhlOdVEAMaCDc1MDA1NjcxIPmCgI4GMAA4qQVADXIJNTA3MjU4MzI2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"131 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-40777823a961bac47d33f4cc1c17d79b_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1640041769.033928","card_id":"Q_507190131","target":{"id":507190131,"title":"2021 年内娱偶像大面积塌房，我们还需要什么样的偶像？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/507190131","type":"question","created":1639930545,"answer_count":80,"follower_count":156,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1497,1718,4146,1548596,1848662],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IjO27uMfhlOdVEAMaCDc0OTkwNTAzILG1/Y0GMAA4nAFADnIJNTA3MTkwMTMxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"103 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-905c5d866e2d314b11fdec00a56f3f49_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1640041769.0342648","card_id":"Q_507116648","target":{"id":507116648,"title":"美剧《切尔诺贝利》拍的怎么样？为何能获得高分？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/507116648","type":"question","created":1639902213,"answer_count":104,"follower_count":161,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[316,114481,404781],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IjO27uMfhlOdVEAMaCDc0OTc0MjAxIIXY+40GMAA4oQFAD3IJNTA3MTE2NjQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"97 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnai